<HL>
   Who's News --
   Monaghan Does an About-Face:
   It's Time to Sell Part of Domino's
   ----
   By Neal Templin
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
03/02/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B1
</SO>
<MS>
CONSUMER CYCLICAL (CYC)
</MS>
<IN>
